PARAMETERS
brush	A Brush object used to construct the plot
name	A string representing the name of the plot
plotStyle	A PlotStyle object used to construct the style of the plot. Possible values:
PlotStyle.Bar
PlotStyle.Block
PlotStyle.Cross
